author: Asa Fitch
title: Stabbling Attack Leaves Two Israelis Wounded, Police Shoot Dead Assailant
text:
DUBAI—A stabbing attack Saturday morning in Jerusalem left two Israelis wounded, extending the worst period of Israeli-Palestinian violence since last year’s war in the Gaza Strip.
The stabbing, which police said was carried out by a 16-year-old Arab, was the 12th such incident since Wednesday in Israel and the West Bank. All but one of them have been carried out by Palestinians or Israeli Arabs against Israeli Jews.
